    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>On El-capitan, giving the below path worked for me:\n<code>Program=\"open /Applications/TextEdit.app/Contents/MacOS/TextEdit\";</code></p>\n\n<p>You can Navigate into the <code>TextEdit.app</code> folder from a terminal window and make sure you have the executable in the right place before trying it out.</p>\n\n<p>Also, you need to change the setting of command like this:\n<code>Command = Program+ \" \"+File_Path;</code></p>\n"
