    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Starting macOS Catalina, system applications are in the <code>/System/Applications</code> folder — <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT210650\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://support.apple.com/HT210650</a></p>\n<p>New path to TextEdit:<br />\n<code>/System/Applications/TextEdit.app/Contents/MacOS/TextEdit</code></p>\n"
